import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['Date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['Date'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['Date'])]
    sns.set_style("darkgrid")
    ax = sns.lineplot(x="Date", y="CO2", data=data, color='blue')
    ax.set(xlabel='Date', ylabel='CO2')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45)
    plt.title('What is the trend of CO2 levels over time?', wrap=True)
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

```
import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['Date'] = pd.to_datetime(data['Date'], format='%Y-%m-%d', errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['Date'])]
    sns.set_style("darkgrid")
    fig, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(12, 6))
    sns.lineplot(x='Date', y='CO2', data=data, ax=ax, label='CO2')
    sns.lineplot(x='Date', y='adjusted_CO2', data=data, ax=ax, label='Adjusted CO2')
    plt.xticks(rotation=45, ha='right')
    plt.title('What is the difference between CO2 and adjusted CO2 levels?', wrap=True)
    plt.legend()
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

```
import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    sns.histplot(data=data, x='CO2', kde=True, color='blue')
    plt.axvline(data['CO2'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label='Mean CO2: {:.2f}'.format(data['CO2'].mean()))
    plt.axvline(data['CO2'].median(), color='green', linestyle='dashed', linewidth=1, label='Median CO2: {:.2f}'.format(data['CO2'].median()))
    plt.legend()
    plt.title('What is the distribution of CO2 levels?', wrap=True)
    plt.xlabel('CO2 Levels')
    plt.ylabel('Frequency')
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```

import seaborn as sns
import pandas as pd
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

def plot(data: pd.DataFrame):
    data['Year'] = pd.to_datetime(data['Year'], format='%Y', errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['Year'])]
    data['Year'] = data['Year'].dt.strftime('%Y')
    data['CO2'] = pd.to_numeric(data['CO2'], errors='coerce')
    data = data[pd.notna(data['CO2'])]
    data = data.groupby('Year').mean().reset_index()
    ax = sns.barplot(x='Year', y='CO2', data=data, color='blue')
    ax.axhline(y=data['CO2'].mean(), color='red', linestyle='--', label='Average CO2 level')
    ax.set(xlabel='Year', ylabel='Average CO2 level')
    plt.legend()
    return plt

chart = plot(data)
```
